Contacts API
===========

This API provides CRUD operations for a collection of contacts stored in a MongoDB database.

Base URL
--------

The base URL for the API is `https://cse341-spring23-3b0l.onrender.com`.

Create Contact
--------------

To create a new contact, send a POST request to https://cse341-spring23-3b0l.onrender.com/contacts with the following JSON setup:


{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "johndoe@example.com",
    "favorite color": "Red",
    "Birthday": 2020-01-31
}
The API will respond with the new contact object, including its unique ID:
{
    "_id": "601f20e1b95c4277c9826e0d",
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "johndoe@example.com",
    "favorite color": "Red",
    "Birthday": 2020-01-31
}

