Get Contact by First Name
To retrieve a single contact by its ID, send a GET request to the URL https://cse341-spring23-3b0l.onrender.com/search?firstName= with the contact first name appended to the URL:
https://cse341-spring23-3b0l.onrender.com/search?firstName=Nick
